{"tid":2451940,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Drive取消無限儲存空間無人講?","createTime":"2021-03-18T12:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T14:50:43.000Z","uid":74368,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2eef56391fe333693d0a4bc03eeed21852cf384","tid":2451940,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"免費Google Drive教育版也取消無限儲存空間，一間學校將設 100TB 上限<br />\n<br />\n眾多大學愛用的 Google Workspace for Education 過往提供無上限容量供符合資格的使用者使用，不過根據 Google Workspace 的最新說明，<span class=\"red\">預計 2022 年 7 月之後將限制 100TB 的使用上限。</span><br />\n<br />\n容量限制政策上路之後，各個機構能有多少儲存空間使用視購買的授權數量而定。<br />\n<br />\n如果是購買 Google Workspace for Education Fundamentals（舊稱 G Suite 教育版）的機構，可獲得至少 100 TB 的集區雲端儲存空間，供機構共同使用，須注意的是，所有檔案都會計入這個額度，包括 Google 雲端硬碟和相簿檔案，以及 Gmail。<br />\n<br />\n如果是購買 Google Workspace for Education Plus（舊稱 G Suite Enterprise 教育版）的機構，每購買一份 Google Workspace for Education Plus 授權，共用集區就會另外獲得 20GB 的儲存空間。如果是繼續使用 G Suite Enterprise 教育版授權客戶，只要每購買一份付費員工授權，共用集區就會另外獲得 100 GB 的儲存空間。<br />\n<br />\n    舉例來說，某某大學如果購買了 5,000 份 G Suite Enterprise 教育版授權，儲存空間就會是 100 TB（基本儲存空間）+（5,000 份授權 x 100 GB = 500TB）= 600TB 的可用儲存空間。<br />\n<br />\n針對管理者 Google 也提供一系列的因應辦法供管理者查看儲存空間的使用狀況，包含可以分析離群值的帳戶報告來查看那些使用者使用了最多容量，或是使用 BigQuery 查看儲存空間用量，也可以考慮將資料轉移到 Google Cloud Storage 等，如果需要進一步的輔助可以查看 Google Workspace 說明。<br />\n<br />\n如果是校友但不確定母校用什麼方案的話，相信過陣子就會收到母校的通知信，告知校友該怎麼處理存在 Google Workspace 裡的資料了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/84550-google-workspace-for-education\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F84550-google-workspace-for-education&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2QxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=4916542a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/84550-google-workspace-for-education</a>"},{"pid":"9db7200821300fcff8275398916dfd523fbd6a00","tid":2451940,"uid":242805,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似已經講咗一排<br />\n係你冇留意"},{"pid":"43d0a82d1b028d1398694fa883a75748e808208b","tid":2451940,"uid":280593,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"Old news..."},{"pid":"2ceb2731512b2b677f5ca5eead294cc08fcffd8c","tid":2451940,"uid":275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"好耐之前，呢度已經有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd5d2a0374669dcb23f78ea83e6d6f08063d9b4","tid":2451940,"uid":335664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:12:45.000Z","msg":"我啲av<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80332007fdc70a73185415f8ed62d9e189ea4310","tid":2451940,"uid":242805,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"其實好想串你，但係由於我係一個有禮貌嘅人所以串都費事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183ca804b58202baad23b8a35f56384bc50d08ab","tid":2451940,"uid":222140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"比開788買2TB<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a30a10c0e5426963e27263508a8327602d5a409","tid":2451940,"uid":61967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"183ca804b58202baad23b8a35f56384bc50d08ab","tid":2451940,"uid":222140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"比開788買2TB<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":